Name: Climb
About the game: You thought you were the only rock climbing hipster around, but these mountains are full of them. Eliminate all competition and claim your rock! Climb, an online multiplayer brawler with short and action packed game sessions! We are releasing Climb to the public to see if a fast paced deathmatch game is what the players want (also because it is fun to play!). We seek your feedback and wishes for upcoming features such as: Mechanics Levels Steam functions (workshop, leaderboards, achievements, etc) Customization items etc See you in the forums!
